- [ ] 回 function creates instances from TypeSchema
- [ ] $ alias exports identical function
- [ ] Validates data against schema on creation
- [ ] Throws ValidationError for invalid data
- [ ] Supports partial instances when specified
- [ ] Type inference flows from schema to instance
- [ ] Instances are immutable (Object.freeze)
- [ ] RED phase tests (workers-0ztzg) pass

